{"type":"message","id":"544fea01","parentId":"5b3fa488","timestamp":"2026-04-05T14:39:23.528Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No memory files exist yet - this is a fresh workspace. I can now greet HALEI. Let me note that BOOTSTRAP.md exists, which means this is a first run situation. I should greet HALEI and start a conversation to figure out who I am and what they need.","thinkingSignature":"060b575ab989cd2e1b2f387b4c1962e29e25014c3b456e84fc8189f37459c68a"},{"type":"text","text":"你好，HALEI。首次见面，我刚上线。\n\n看起来这是一个全新的 workspace——没有记忆，没有配置，甚至还没有名字。我们可以花一两分钟快速对齐：你想让我扮演什么角色？目前你在用的是 `product-selector` 模式，你希望我变成什么？直接告诉我你的需求或者让我们先把这个\"大总管\"的身份定下来。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1641,"output":135,"cacheRead":12515,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14291,"cost":{"input":0.0004923,"output":0.00016199999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0007509,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0014052000000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775399959167,"responseId":"0621a717f3930ca4227e4f88b281092c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"31369279","parentId":"544fea01","timestamp":"2026-04-05T14:40:28.966Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-05 22:39:24 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b521375cb68a0c245e8b39b9a868]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b521375cb68a0c245e8b39b9a868\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-05 22:37 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n你不是有一个可以搜索17个网站的skill吗，可以看看好几天了"}],"timestamp":1775400028828}}
{"type":"message","id":"9bfa1e78","parentId":"31369279","timestamp":"2026-04-05T14:40:34.222Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about a skill that can search 17 websites. Looking at the available skills, I can see there's a skill called \"multi-search-engine\" that matches this description. Let me read it.","thinkingSignature":"9b32449cc495c01df8ad7af86cc94941ef9e627a8eefcad2a19f8ff06c4a2093"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qtj1g2unpuyk_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multi-search-engine/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39,"output":87,"cacheRead":12536,"cacheWrite":1896,"totalTokens":14558,"cost":{"input":0.0000117,"output":0.00010439999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00075216,"cacheWrite":0.000711,"total":0.0015792599999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775400028837,"responseId":"0621a75da14837f3784e4f3ecf41a642"}}
{"type":"message","id":"edc64bb7","parentId":"9bfa1e78","timestamp":"2026-04-05T14:40:34.258Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qtj1g2unpuyk_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: \"multi-search-engine\"\ndescription: \"Multi search engine integration with 17 engines (8 CN + 9 Global). Supports advanced search operators, time filters, site search, privacy engines, and WolframAlpha knowledge queries. No API keys required.\"\n---\n\n# Multi Search Engine v2.0.1\n\nIntegration of 17 search engines for web crawling without API keys.\n\n## Search Engines\n\n### Domestic (8)\n- **Baidu**: `https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}`\n- **Bing CN**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=0`\n- **Bing INT**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=1`\n- **360**: `https://www.so.com/s?q={keyword}`\n- **Sogou**: `https://sogou.com/web?query={keyword}`\n- **WeChat**: `https://wx.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&query={keyword}`\n- **Toutiao**: `https://so.toutiao.com/search?keyword={keyword}`\n- **Jisilu**: `https://www.jisilu.cn/explore/?keyword={keyword}`\n\n### International (9)\n- **Google**: `https://www.google.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Google HK**: `https://www.google.com.hk/search?q={keyword}`\n- **DuckDuckGo**: `https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q={keyword}`\n- **Yahoo**: `https://search.yahoo.com/search?p={keyword}`\n- **Startpage**: `https://www.startpage.com/sp/search?query={keyword}`\n- **Brave**: `https://search.brave.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Ecosia**: `https://www.ecosia.org/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Qwant**: `https://www.qwant.com/?q={keyword}`\n- **WolframAlpha**: `https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i={keyword}`\n\n## Quick Examples\n\n```javascript\n// Basic search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=python+tutorial\"})\n\n// Site-specific\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=site:github.com+react\"})\n\n// File type\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=machine+learning+filetype:pdf\"})\n\n// Time filter (past week)\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=ai+news&tbs=qdr:w\"})\n\n// Privacy search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=privacy+tools\"})\n\n// DuckDuckGo Bangs\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=!gh+tensorflow\"})\n\n// Knowledge calculation\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i=100+USD+to+CNY\"})\n```\n\n## Advanced Operators\n\n| Operator | Example | Description |\n|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `site:` | `site:github.com python` | Search within site |\n| `filetype:` | `filetype:pdf report` | Specific file type |\n| `\"\"` | `\"machine learning\"` | Exact match |\n| `-` | `python -snake` | Exclude term |\n| `OR` | `cat OR dog` | Either term |\n\n## Time Filters\n\n| Parameter | Description |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| `tbs=qdr:h` | Past hour |\n| `tbs=qdr:d` | Past day |\n| `tbs=qdr:w` | Past week |\n| `tbs=qdr:m` | Past month |\n| `tbs=qdr:y` | Past year |\n\n## Privacy Engines\n\n- **DuckDuckGo**: No tracking\n- **Startpage**: Google results + privacy\n- **Brave**: Independent index\n- **Qwant**: EU GDPR compliant\n\n## Bangs Shortcuts (DuckDuckGo)\n\n| Bang | Destination |\n|------|-------------|\n| `!g` | Google |\n| `!gh` | GitHub |\n| `!so` | Stack Overflow |\n| `!w` | Wikipedia |\n| `!yt` | YouTube |\n\n## WolframAlpha Queries\n\n- Math: `integrate x^2 dx`\n- Conversion: `100 USD to CNY`\n- Stocks: `AAPL stock`\n- Weather: `weather in Beijing`\n\n## Documentation\n\n- `references/advanced-search.md` - Domestic search guide\n- `references/international-search.md` - International search guide\n- `CHANGELOG.md` - Version history\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775400034252}}
{"type":"message","id":"2af4bd48","parentId":"edc64bb7","timestamp":"2026-04-05T14:40:39.795Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about searching 17 websites. Based on the skill, I have a multi-search-engine skill that can search 17 engines (8 CN + 9 global). The user said \"可以看看好几天了\" which seems to mean \"it's been a few days\" or \"can check a few days\". But it's a bit ambiguous - maybe they want me to check something from a few days ago, or they want to search with a time filter (past few days).\n\nLet me ask what they want to search about. I'll respond in Chinese since that's what they're using.","thinkingSignature":"7c007da4ecfb9db863a19941dc034d96ddbfd5395d7911ee3ceb272c19b44173"},{"type":"text","text":"有，17个搜索引擎（8个国内 + 9个国际），可以指定时间范围搜索。\n\n你想搜什么？关键词发我，我来查。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3030,"output":153,"cacheRead":12515,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15698,"cost":{"input":0.000909,"output":0.0001836,"cacheRead":0.0007509,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018435}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775400034259,"responseId":"0621a762fa28455aa4faa43c8b3fe9de"}}
