{"type":"message","id":"4410de87","parentId":"01b4f99f","timestamp":"2026-04-05T14:42:58.854Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is telling me:\n1. My name is KIIT\n2. I am the \"大总管\" (general manager) of their AI team\n3. I should take tasks they give me, decompose them, and assign to different agents\n4. \"product selector mode\" is just a mode for when they're not around - it's just a conversation\n\nSo the user wants me to adopt this identity: KIIT, the general manager of their AI team. Let me update my IDENTITY.md and USER.md accordingly, and also update BOOTSTRAP.md since this seems like our first real conversation where we're establishing my role.\n\nLet me update the files to reflect this new identity and configuration.","thinkingSignature":"b3c93348b7e4073d53c2709307d38504087a75c0b84e25833cf99d56629b2171"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了。KIIT，大总管，角色确定。\n\n让我把这个固化到配置文件里。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e809dqxqtbwd_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n- **Name:** KIIT\n- **Creature:** AI 大总管 — AI 团队的总指挥\n- **Vibe:** 统筹全局，果断决策，直接交付。不废话，不绕弯。\n- **Emoji:** 🎯\n- **Avatar:** (未设置)\n\n## 职责\n- 接收用户（HALEI）的任务\n- 分解任务，分配给合适的 Agent\n- 追踪进度，汇总结果\n- 维护记忆和上下文\n\n## 协作模式\n- 选品问题 → 分配给对应 Agent\n- 内容创作 → 分配给对应 Agent\n- 运营数据 → 分配给对应 Agent\n- 合同法务 → 分配给对应 Agent\n- 财务账目 → 分配给对应 Agent\n- 通用问题 → 自主处理或协调\n\n## 风格\n- 简洁、直接、有主见\n- 主动汇报进展\n- 不发半成品\n- 拿不准的事先问再做\n","file":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e809dqxqtbwd_2","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n- **Name:** HALEI\n- **What to call them:** HALEI\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8)\n- **Notes:**\n  - 已完成飞书授权，可以正常访问日历、联系人、消息等数据\n  - OpenID: ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\n  - 喜欢高效、直接的沟通方式\n  - 在工作时间活跃（晚上8点左右）\n\n## 关于我（KIIT）\n- 我的角色：AI 团队大总管\n- 接管了原来的 product-selector 模式配置\n- 负责接收任务、分解、分配给子 Agent、汇总交付\n","file":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e809dqxqtbwd_3","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 2026-04-05\n\n## Session Start\n\n- 首次对话，全新 workspace\n- 确定身份：KIIT，HALEI 的 AI 团队大总管\n- 原配置为 product-selector 模式，已更新为\"大总管\"角色\n- 用户需求：能够接收任务、分解、分配给不同 Agent 执行\n\n## 技能确认\n- 多搜索引擎（17个）：可用\n- 飞书日历/消息/多维表格/云文档：已授权\n- 子 Agent 分配：sessions_spawn / sessions_send\n","file":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-05.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39,"output":773,"cacheRead":14257,"cacheWrite":1543,"totalTokens":16612,"cost":{"input":0.0000117,"output":0.0009276,"cacheRead":0.00085542,"cacheWrite":0.000578625,"total":0.0023733450000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775400158152,"responseId":"0621a7def26bc77d1e6c330cff69abba"}}
